# Astro reads env from site/.env (gitignored). Copy this to site/.env and fill in.
#
# MapTiler API key for the maps. It is a CLIENT-side, DOMAIN-RESTRICTED key — it
# ships in the page HTML by design, so it is NOT a secret — but keep it out of
# git. Locally it goes in site/.env; for the deploy, set it as a Cloudflare Pages
# environment variable. Restrict the key to your domain (photos.example.com,
# plus localhost for dev) in the MapTiler dashboard so the public value can't be
# reused elsewhere. Without it the maps show a "set PUBLIC_MAPTILER_KEY" notice.
PUBLIC_MAPTILER_KEY=
